cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CE, cs.IT 

The paper discusses the development and deployment of a mobile application for taxi transport, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybernetics (cs.CY) in terms of designing and evaluating the app's user interface and user experience. The app also relies on information technology (cs.IT) for real-time data processing and analysis. Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges and insights gained from deploying the app in two different cities, which involves issues related to social and economic systems (cs.SI) and complex systems (cs.CE).
